{"lang": "ja_JP", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "背理分光", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "16-9", "avgTag": "戦闘前", "storyName": "狂人の弁解", "storyInfo": "坑夫のリーダー・ランキンが見る悪夢の中では、彼らは近衛兵を殺してはいなかった。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$m_bat_act37d0d0_02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g4_miningarea_polluted", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いや……やめて……", "name": "若い坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_attack_heavy", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "うっ！", "name": "若い坑夫"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたは、うら若い女性が目の前で倒れ彼女の死体からゆっくりと黒い槍が「生えて」くるのを見た。"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "すぐに動かなくなったその身体の横では、別の者が両足をばたつかせながら、この危険な場所から逃れようとしている。"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ば、化け物……！", "name": "怯える坑夫"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_wtchkgopenftstp", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_blacksmoke_01", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_29", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黒がとめどなく迫ってくる。黒、黒、黒。何もかもが黒く、ただ血だけが赤い。あなたは目の前のものが生きているのかどうかさえも判断できなかった。"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恐れるな――退くな！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "まだ動ける者、立ち上がれ――", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ああ！！！！", "name": "坑夫"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黒は止まらない。屍の山と血の海を踏み分けて進んでいく。地面には坑夫や、衛兵、一般のウルサス人が横たわっている。"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "絶え間ない悲鳴を聞いたあなたは悟った。振り返って逃げようと逃げまいと、あのどこからともなく現れる矛にいずれは追いつかれると。"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "そのため、あなたはただ見ているしかなかった。無数の骸を貫いた矛が大地から突き上がり、地面をほとんど覆い尽くす様を。"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_daggerslow", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突然、すべての矛が屍の山から引き抜かれ、黒い影の手の中で一本の長剣に再構築された。"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "それから、その正体不明の声の主は手に持った長剣を高々と掲げると、あなたに向けてきた。"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g4_miningarea_polluted", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お前は立ったまま死ぬことを望んでいるのか。", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "いいや……俺は死なない……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "こんなところで死んでたまるか。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "悪くない望みだ。", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "しかし残念ながら、叶わぬ願いだ。", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_oldman_walk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1964_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あれは……？", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_077"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキン、助けに来たぞ！", "name": "軍人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキン――", "name": "軍人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お前たち――レーニャ、なぜここに？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あんたを助けに来たんだ！", "name": "軍人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "お前たち、助けにきてくれたのか！　俺の戦友、お前たちもここに――", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "力を合わせて戦おう。あの頃と同じように！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あの頃と同じように！", "name": "軍人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "さあ！　奴を囲め、あの頃と同じように！　一人倒れたら、別の一人がそいつのいた場所を埋めるんだ。一つの集団が倒れたら、別の集団がそいつらの場所を埋めるんだ！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺の後に続け！", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_077"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愚かな……", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたは背後から熱が伝わってくるのを感じた。焼けつくような感覚が全身へ広がる。熱はあなたの血を沸き立たせ、視界がはっきりとした。彼らはあなたの名を叫び、あなたを前へと押し出す。"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "その堅固な人だかりに支えられ、あなたは跳び上がると、黒い胴体の胸と思しき場所へ向けて――"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "突き立てた。"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 3.0, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.0, "xScaleTo": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.2, "duration": 3.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_audience_chaos", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.8, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleTo": 1.8, "duration": 0.4, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.4, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "x": 0.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.6, "yScaleFrom": 1.6, "xScaleTo": 1.5, "yScaleTo": 1.5, "duration": 10.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.1}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_piercechest", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 50.0, "ystrength": 50.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――死ね――", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ふっ……", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "血の滴る音も、痙攣の反応もない。"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "刃を阻む抵抗だけが少しずつ弱まり、やがて完全に失われた。"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i01", "screenadapt": "coverall", "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "なるほど……そうだったか……", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……「ガブリエルス」――", "name": "「皇帝の利刃」"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後の音を吐き出すと、黒い影に支えられていた制服は、突然力を失ったかのように抵抗を見せなくなった。"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたがその化け物に終わりを与えた。勇気、決断力、度胸によって。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "存在しない「友人」の支えによって。"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_5_7_shining", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_atmosphere_horror", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "at"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "ハァ……ハァ……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "両腕が重い。ここはどこだ？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「――倒れた、倒れたぞ！」"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "……誰が？", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「ランキン、お前が――俺たちが、俺たちがやったんだ――」"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「奴を殺したんだ！！」"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "誰を殺したって？　この黒い……雪は……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "いや、まだ足りない。道を塞ぐ者が一人死んだところで、そこら中を埋め尽くす、この鬱陶しい雪は……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "どうしたって消えやしないんだ。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「ランキン、ランキン？　これからどうすればいい？」"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "「ランキン――」"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_tinnitus", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 0.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {"direction": 4.0, "fillfrom": 0.01, "fillto": 0.2, "fadetime": 0.1}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_newiceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.4, "yScale": 1.4, "y": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "backgroundTween", "attributes": {"xFrom": 200.0, "duration": 30.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "bg_newiceforest_2", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "duration": 0.1, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.1, "bend": 0.3, "posfrom": "0,-160", "posto": "0,-160", "duration": 4.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "action": "zoom", "poszoom": "0.5,0.5", "scale": 1.4, "duration": 0.0}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_whitemask", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "focusparam", "attributes": {"blur": "false", "effect": "Grayscale"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.3, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキン！", "name": "軍人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺は……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "ランキン！　ランキン！", "name": "坑夫"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "波のような人だかりがあなたに押し寄せてきた。彼らはあなたを持ち上げたかと思うと、また引きずり下ろす。この浮遊感は、前にも覚えがあった。"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人々の歓声、叫び声。耳をつんざくような反響の中、ここにいるはずのない人があなたの名前を呼んだ。"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "――ランキン――", "name": "軍人？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1976_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_whitemask", "layer": 2.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "focusparam", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "curtain", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "あなたは目を閉じ、その言葉に導かれるままあの森の中へと帰っていく。辺境駐屯軍の一部隊、帰還できるはずのない任務。"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "今、あなたがいる場所はそこではない。"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "勝った……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "俺たちは勝ったんだ。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_atmosphere_horror", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "at"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.5, "channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"type": "bg", "id": "bg_newiceforest_2", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "duration": 4.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g16_smokeonblackgroud", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "持ち上げられ、また落ちる瞬間、あなたはいまだ消えきらぬ黒い塵を遠くに見た。"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "at", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "「黒い雪」"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黒い煙が、まるで無数の細くうねる根のように、制服のあらゆる隙間から這い出てくる。それは貪るように絡みつき、覆い、吸いついて、やがて制服を完全に包み込んだ。"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "黒い煙に包まれた制服は、再びゆっくりと人の形を成し始めた。まるで――"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_smokeconverge", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_30", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.2, "yScale": 1.2, "fadetime": 3.0}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.2, "yScaleFrom": 1.2, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "初めから死んでなどいなかったかのように。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}